{"tid":2262771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐韓美軍A-10攻擊機 南韓上空誤投飛行武器","createTime":"2020-10-29T10:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T11:11:05.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"52fe53fab8adcdf051e27d3846475b0bd48856b7","tid":2262771,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"駐韓美軍一架A-10雷霆二式攻擊機（Thunderbolt II，暱稱疣豬）本月中旬進行演訓時，在江原道寧越郡上空意外投下一種非爆炸性飛行武器，消息近日才曝光，據悉，該武器至今尚未被尋回，但應不致構成重大影響。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，駐防於烏山空軍基地的美國空軍第51戰鬥機聯隊發言人德拉菲中尉（Laniel R. de LaFe）表示，一架美軍A-10攻擊機本月13日進行常規飛行訓練時，疏忽地釋放了非導向、非爆炸性的飛行武器。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生後，美軍第51戰鬥機聯隊及南韓國軍成員聯手在相關地區搜尋失落武器，在連續3日搜尋未果後，雙方一致認定「考量到撞擊地點與地形，應不致有重大威脅」，搜尋任務宣告終止。<br />\n<br />\n德拉菲中尉表示，有關當局正對事件進行安全調查，同時研議是否修改相關機制，以避免類似事件再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3335542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3335542&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KilSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=93b95a54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3335542&h=0321b5cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3335542</a><br />\n<br />\n韓聯社:<a href=\"https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20201029007400325?section=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FAEN20201029007400325%3Fsection%3Dnews&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KilSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=1468e27d\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20201029007400325?section=news</a>"},{"pid":"ac7a70121f66be62480a046cda462a8f905328d2","tid":2262771,"uid":10056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"之前係咪又係駐韓美軍炸死左個平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91648fde1eaf05abf38029eb51e022cf793e7cc","tid":2262771,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:52:09.000Z","